name: equalization - glitch
description:
An accidental display glitch created by some sort of error in objkt.com's Creations view of my hic et nunc mint "equalization" (OBJKT #275773). The original was created in Unity 3D, with the VFX Graph particle engine. This glitch was recorded with a screen recorder, and turned in to an animated GIF in Adobe Premier. 

I like this one because the original is one of my few works without a circle motif, and this glitch adds it, as if it was supposed to be there all along, and I just forgot it.
